Author: Rivka90
Text: I feel this. I walk around the grocery store muttering to myself "this fucking sucks" because I can't justify any of the food but I WANT to be able to just pick something up and not think about it at all. That effortless ease that everyone around me seems to have regarding food and weight, while I'm over here looking at labels and leaving empty handed. You are not alone ðŸ’“
